## 10. Flow Diagram

```
User Request (Claude Code)
  ↓
X-Brain-Agent-Type Header / metadata.user_id
  ↓ [identity-resolver.ts]
  ├→ parseMetadataUserId() → extract userHash, accountId, sessionId
