  └→ Return McpAuthResult { agentType: AgentType, ... }
  ↓
[Tool Execution: iam/authority.ts]
  ├→ Get agentType from context (or derive via ACTOR_DEFAULT_AGENT_TYPE)
  ├→ checkAuthority(agentType, action)
  │   ├→ Check human bypass
  │   ├→ Query authorized_to edges (per-identity overrides)
  │   └→ Query authority_scope table (global defaults)
  └→ Return: auto | provisional | propose | blocked
```

